Scientific Results of a Journey in Central Asia, 1899-1902 : vol.2

description.@value: 第2巻：クルック=タグとクルック=ダリヤ、カラ=コシュン、ロプ沙漠、ロプ=ノール問題、および中央アジアの沙漠・砂丘・沙に関する記述、タリム水系の水路学的検討、さらに東トルキスタンの住民、楼蘭の遺跡に関する記述も含む。

Vol. 2: An account of Kuruk-Tag, Kuruk-Darya (Kum-Daria) , Khara-Kushun, the Lop Desert, the Lop Nor (“wandering lake”) issue; as well as the deserts, sand dunes and sands of Central Asia. The work also includes a scholarly investigation into the canals and water system of the Tarim River, as well as descriptions of the people in Turkestan and the ruins at Loulan.
